long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: You can search your browser history for GitHub URL you visited. This helps you to find and open GitHub repository, issues, pull requests, or etc. Just type "git" and press tab key in your Chrome's address bar.
